{"tid":1965463,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"宣告將會自殺的女孩","createTime":"2020-04-09T13:06:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T14:53:59.000Z","uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fbad5882c8298556ee74c2f0d915102f78098336","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:06:52.000Z","msg":"啊～總有一天我會尋死。<br />\n大概是在某天，天空湛藍的日子。"},{"pid":"9d3ab7a5c5c9031ad8805bd7ea901f687f1013bc","tid":1965463,"uid":331838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:08:16.000Z","msg":"好句～好句～"},{"pid":"c69bebcfc916cd78a01546a377bfbec95f26de6c","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T09:46:56.000Z","msg":"我有過因小事而滿足的日子，夏蟬，春雨和綠葉上的甘露。"},{"pid":"0c2afaa91533abc6516aa22742562f1eb3e4ec5f","tid":1965463,"uid":332656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T22:31:57.000Z","msg":"樓主啊～ 當你想放棄生命的時候，<br />\n希望你能發現，<br />\n能擁有生命，是幸福的。"},{"pid":"828c41b80cd3ad0a615d2da992d5930928851b41","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T07:11:15.000Z","msg":"我也有過因小事而抱怨的日子，鐵鏽，霉菌和屏幕上的劃痕。"},{"pid":"de7f91a3620d37f8042ac7d07c6bd2fe0a37582e","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:35:54.000Z","msg":"日子因實在而無奈。人生因無奈而實在。"},{"pid":"e452a3e4bb7662767601e0d96dc68356930a462a","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T06:55:40.000Z","msg":"時間可以把所有都殺死..."},{"pid":"7a55aa728a7002b7f1335146b638ae4ef697c682","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:28:03.000Z","msg":"那含羞的笑容，那想吻你的衝動。那擁抱的溫暖，還有那最該死的記憶。"},{"pid":"eeb21ca8c815f7d8278985b68e6fdfaf69b82e65","tid":1965463,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbad5882c8298556ee74c2f0d915102f78098336","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:06:52.000Z","msg":"啊～總有一天我會尋死。<br />\n大概是在某天，天空湛藍的日子。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T10:58:37.000Z","msg":"看來你心中的痛苦，已令你覺得生無可戀．．．人生之中往往有很多重要的決定，而自殺肯定是人一生中最矛盾、最痛苦，也是最重大的決定。我相信，自殺不是你想選擇的，更不是你唯一的選擇，只不過你所面對的困境和痛苦好像超越了你所能應付的，是嗎？<br />\n <br />\n無論你將會如何打算你的前路，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，好像氣球裡積存的壓力一樣。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVa9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=e7fb92b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（<a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVa9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=6d4b7c58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php）。</a> 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n <br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"ca148980de5477e404f033964228a21ce4701545","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:20:46.000Z","msg":"沒有成為你心目中的大人吧！沒關係，我也是一如既往的糟糕。"},{"pid":"cf3283c520e2a102cb3080c7585d8b6412ab36fe","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:16:53.000Z","msg":"別再期盼甚麼，今天是你曾經憧憬的未來啊。"},{"pid":"0593cff2a4d5f2f5ac7e7ee0d48dce4e87cfc015","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T07:18:03.000Z","msg":"據說情愛是人世間幸福的泉源。說白了，我只是想隨便談個戀愛。"},{"pid":"11f2e9061a171035f31c9aadd2a16d6394d9de24","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:57:55.000Z","msg":"卻一不小心，太認真了。"},{"pid":"dbc3b8067c5a1f9a28f07149bd3032249b8fec94","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T08:44:03.000Z","msg":"往日輕狂的我呀，能否帶給我擄心的顫抖。"},{"pid":"d365a51798e5e16ffbc8762e9c8d2c2504b425e7","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T12:19:30.000Z","msg":"這世界有太多病症，卻沒有一種神奇的藥能醫百病。"},{"pid":"6c3123e18f93f3e18a833a889cad8babe68ca4a3","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T09:07:02.000Z","msg":"人死了或會轉世，重新開始，卻這世界不會死，沒有一個重生的可能。"},{"pid":"de98a24344332ff4b92cdb09ecd3aaec8413b203","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:23:00.000Z","msg":"大概厭了世，天空還會褪點色。卻灰階最讓人有感覺。"},{"pid":"2a6f82212eeb3b8cd30d17527b6878248db3c40e","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T07:45:21.000Z","msg":"人生之中別忘了最重要的東西，發夢的空間。"},{"pid":"9f7556f6bb0257cebada14caed407bfacfa886ce","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:53:52.000Z","msg":"從來不慣死神睜眼睛相看，只是日子來到，不忍心就這樣走掉。"},{"pid":"90ce234ab7d369312e39a8f215ed60e068ce6f4f","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T09:08:31.000Z","msg":"說錯了再見，那就只能說懷念。"},{"pid":"2f113ba0778629da5cc08e2b45aa91cd1f526007","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T07:29:47.000Z","msg":"世上最強的烈酒，也無法令哀傷永遠沉睡...拿起酒水，灌下去。"},{"pid":"18561205372b57ec484bd18cbab3163fc6163efe","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:16:03.000Z","msg":"雖非偉大詩人，卻有幸得人觀我這齣獨腳雅戲。"},{"pid":"eadf467d7020331b1275eace0badcaafe7c1aae5","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T07:24:50.000Z","msg":"再努力也敵不過天意。"},{"pid":"24d40f840121e6a4993a90b6ebfc11cdf578c30a","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:40:06.000Z","msg":"百年草木，歷盡時代，還是被無情砍伐。到底有生命卻沒感受是怎樣的存在？"},{"pid":"5d1be19e04289adf436627600c1919dd4da63c6a","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T07:30:50.000Z","msg":"心臟懷念著夏天的餘溫，卻腳下沙土冷若冰霜，心也隨之麻木了。"},{"pid":"2b94cc546b5541dc9b424924ffd78b7937b30219","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T09:35:57.000Z","msg":"演員謝幕，觀者離座。"},{"pid":"4549c311e1b57eaad8f775bee9bfb11c82c5ca68","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:25:41.000Z","msg":"有盡世界所有時間，卻怎麼也留不住這一刻，像瀑布洪水，一湧傾掉。"},{"pid":"b5572c6acb0485a6930d7f6e7734f3b51cdfe472","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T07:48:53.000Z","msg":"得意人反成失意人。"},{"pid":"2e1a7f37a924c69fc316ab46087d6216bbc53502","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T14:06:31.000Z","msg":"歲月漸漸不像從前美艷，徒留回憶堡壘渡過終點。"},{"pid":"cbb6a0131a1ec7973f986bc1313c106d73afcb5b","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T14:01:54.000Z","msg":"事過境遷，人事已轉變，身邊再沒多少張熟悉的臉。"},{"pid":"b3da6c87f9e6a6365c1eb11b52ad818556e38bf9","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T12:52:09.000Z","msg":"經過這些日子，筆下能寫已所剩無幾，大概沒太多再說了。"},{"pid":"36a46f5abd08fcf75faba8e7f400b4d6f0227bb0","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T16:00:23.000Z","msg":"許多事情都不在乎了，對事情的敏感度也只在零附近徘徊。"},{"pid":"0ff77e2f8922fd45f3eb4736ac48ee424ec1bd7a","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T14:19:17.000Z","msg":"望著街道人流穿梭，幾許面孔上都沒有五官，沒有表情，而連自己也表情不再。"},{"pid":"02cb3e962c957c55f9a5f695ae82174f671de537","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T14:05:25.000Z","msg":"沒甚麼壞不壞，順水了，還那會管甚麼逆流而上。"},{"pid":"90e1c145cb601a235a92d8d6ead9f828563ea172","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:33:54.000Z","msg":"離愁別緒，死亡往往帶給人最悲絕的回憶。"},{"pid":"5f3489e22833e6a54c3243ae6a1f13bb30c5f101","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:17:02.000Z","msg":"自己心痛，也渴望棺木中人能長眠安睡，死者所得到的，在最後是祝福。"},{"pid":"065f6ffa410897011ab23e491451e2a008591cfe","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T14:27:52.000Z","msg":"是否打不破命格，只能目視生命中的過客，只停留一煞。"},{"pid":"3c2e5780774b5cce491937aa6d6eccb900bd641e","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T14:33:21.000Z","msg":"有些畫面覺得很美，但始終，感覺差了點對手戲。"},{"pid":"06e52e0217a9fe7131731189d6f1431585cc0608","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T15:16:15.000Z","msg":"人不講情，講理，這何以有理？"},{"pid":"b7a3b1266cb4b446715e460995097df0fdf432f9","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T14:58:23.000Z","msg":"字畢，緣散。"},{"pid":"4c2bfe6b83e2ef0c1a3600fa39ef8d0ed6df1142","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T16:09:55.000Z","msg":"男人不可沒上進心，女人不可沒上半身。"},{"pid":"49382b3e874a05ab4ba164c774b5c636508f5315","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T16:10:11.000Z","msg":"偶爾做些不習慣的事感覺也不錯，就像每天平靜的湖水有點湧浪，激起水花，感受自己的存在。"},{"pid":"b7c91e8a29faf05fdaa4a84395735c0c0baa8de4","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:34:05.000Z","msg":"總訴說著往日多美好，沉淪於回憶之中。"},{"pid":"05600c79041dfd86a2e8c55b0a08513e7cee4b53","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T13:53:38.000Z","msg":"那秋天的雨正是盛夏的種子。"},{"pid":"487d8279b55fe097e460930b1164e73c86435594","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T14:06:03.000Z","msg":"謊言是美好的，它把別人給蒙蔽，好讓別人免受傷害。"},{"pid":"ce2c87a3d56edbdd64c2b9f6afa867f77a0e62a2","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T15:54:12.000Z","msg":"直至雪花飄落，才驚覺，這一刻感到落寞。"},{"pid":"c4e29fa54d7f817ca3aa1754a0ed50d2ae281575","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:08:14.000Z","msg":"人世如此淡薄，卻能於其中動情，也能於其中絕情。"},{"pid":"84f37936d6571c1d227f837549e1d155c05e7c3d","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T15:12:47.000Z","msg":"大概在人世中忘不了情，大概在人世中不可無情。人世中，濫了情。"},{"pid":"cc2a6ef242ed09f181126c989505e0f97f1db4ac","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:59:46.000Z","msg":"大概沒半天，傷勢沒那麼明顯，眼淚半濺，也算得上歷練。"},{"pid":"3907ab8a4cabef24a0706983685c5e7f0b72b8c0","tid":1965463,"uid":273873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:43:19.000Z","msg":"大概是昨天，決心洗心革面，往事塵煙不再沾邊。"}]}